<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>User Stories - My Music Website</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: sans-serif;
            margin: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .user-story {
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .user-story h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .user-story p {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>User Stories - My Music Website</h1>

    <section class="user-story">
        <h3>User Story 1: Discover Music via SoundCloud Embed</h3>
        <p><strong>As the</strong> website owner (musician), <strong>I want to</strong> embed a SoundCloud player with a featured track directly on the website <strong>so that</strong> visitors can immediately sample my music and get a feel for my style, increasing the likelihood they'll explore more of my work.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="user-story">
        <h3>User Story 2: Navigate to Music on Preferred Platform</h3>
        <p><strong>As the</strong> website owner (musician), <strong>I want to</strong> provide clear and easy-to-find links to my music on various platforms like SoundCloud, Spotify, and Apple Music <strong>so that</strong> fans can easily listen to my music on their preferred streaming service, boosting my streams and visibility on those platforms.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="user-story">
        <h3>User Story 3: Subscribe to Mailing List for Updates</h3>
        <p><strong>As the</strong> website owner (musician), <strong>I want to</strong> include a simple and effective mailing list subscription form <strong>so that</strong> I can collect email addresses from interested fans and directly communicate with them about new releases, events, and other news, fostering a stronger connection and driving engagement.</p>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
